n- `read_token_from_file(file_path)` -- reads a token from a file, returns stripped content or empty string if file not found.\n\n### agentcube/exceptions.py\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/exceptions.py`\n- Defines 4 exception classes:\n  - `AgentCubeError(Exception)` -- base exception\n  - `CommandExecutionError(AgentCubeError)` -- has `exit_code`, `stderr`, `command` attributes\n  - `SessionError(AgentCubeError)` -- for session creation/management failures\n  - `DataPlaneError(AgentCubeError)` -- for data plane operation failures\n\n### agentcube/clients/control_plane.py\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n- `ControlPlaneClient` -- client for the Workload Manager control plane API.\n- Methods: `create_session()`, `delete_session()`, `close()`.\n- Reads Kubernetes service account token from `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` as fallback auth.\n\n### agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n- `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` -- client for the Code Interpreter data plane API via the Router.\n- Methods: `execute_command()`, `run_code()`, `write_file()`, `upload_file()`, `download_file()`, `list_files()`, `close()`.\n\n### agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n- `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` -- client for the Agent Runtime data plane API via the Router.\n- Methods: `bootstrap_session_id()`, `invoke()`, `close()`.\n- Uses `x-agentcube-session-id` header for session tracking.\n\n### agentcube/code_interpreter.py\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n- `CodeInterpreterClient` -- high-level client for Code Interpreter sessions.\n- Creates/manages sessions via ControlPlaneClient and executes code/files via CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient.\n- Methods: `execute_command()`, `run_code()`, `write_file()`, `upload_file()`, `download_file()`, `list_files()`, `stop()`.\n- Supports context manager (`__enter__`/`__exit__`).\n\n### agentcube/agent_runtime.py\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n- `AgentRuntimeClient` -- high-level client for Agent Runtime invocation.\n- Bootstraps sessions and invokes agent workloads through the Router.\n- Methods: `invoke()`, `close()`.\n- Supports context manager (`__enter__`/`__exit__`).\n\n---\n\n## 8. COMPLETE FILE LIST (all source files in python-sdk/, excluding cache/egg-info)\n\n| # | Absolute Path |\n|---|--------------|\n| 1 | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/pyproject.toml` |\n| 2 | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/design.md` |\n| 3 | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/spec.md` |\n| 4 | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/__init__.py` |\n| 5 | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/agent_runtime.py` |\n| 6 | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/code_interpreter.py` |\n| 7 | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/exceptions.py` |\n| 8 | `/home/dsj/